commit.message:
* Make-lang.in, Makefile.in, config-lang.in: GCC, not GNU CC.

From-SVN: r64290

files.patch:

+2003-03-12  Nathanael Nerode  <neroden@gcc.gnu.org>

+	* Make-lang.in, Makefile.in, config-lang.in: GCC, not GNU CC.
+

 	* misc.c (gnat_init): Update for new prototype.
